Titolo: Gran Turismo 6

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: Gran Turismo 6 is a racing video game developed by Polyphony Digital and published by Sony Computer Entertainment for the PlayStation 3. It is the sixth major release and twelfth game overall in the Gran Turismo video game series. It was released worldwide on December 6, 2013. It was met with positive reception and was a financial success. New features included the addition of more cars and tracks, improvements to the car customisation options, and partnerships with the Goodwood Festival of Speed, the Ayrton Senna Institute, the FIA and NASCAR.
Gran Turismo 6 is the first game in history to feature officially FIA-certified content.



Genere: Sim racing

Valutazione: 88
